This testmod produces the raw (unprocessed) E3SM output that the ACE/Samudra
offline pipeline expects as input. It uses the timeSeriesStatsCustom analysis
member in MPAS-O and MPAS-SI for 5-daily ocean/ice output, and standard EAM/ELM
history tapes for 6-hourly atmosphere/land output.

This is the "legacy" output configuration — all postprocessing (horizontal
remapping, vertical coarsening, derived field computation) must be done offline.
Compare with the fme_output testmod which does all postprocessing online.

Use verify_fme_output.py --cross-verify to compare output between the two testmods.
